        Description copied from interface: HttpServerAuthenticationMechanismFactory
        Obtain an instance of the authentication mechanism requested provided this is allowed by any policy specified within the supplied properties.

        createAuthenticationMechanism in interface HttpServerAuthenticationMechanismFactory
